      public boolean withdrawApplication(Applicant applicant)
      Withdraws an Applicant's application. Possible for PENDING, SUCCESSFUL, or BOOKED statuses. Sets the status to UNSUCCESSFUL and clears application details. Increments room count if status was BOOKED.
